Brief installation instructions for pknots 1.06
MAY 2008
------------------------------------------

Source distribution (pknots-1.06.tar.gz):

    tar zxf pknots-1.06.tar.gz       Unpacks the archive. (makes a new directory, pknots-1.06).
    cd pknots-1.06                   Moves into the distribution toplevel directory.
    cd src                           Moves into the directory src.
    cd squid                         Moves into the directory squid.
    make                             Builds the binaries for the squid library. 
    cd ..                            Moves into the source directory.
    make                             Builds the binaries. 
 

It should build cleanly on just about any UNIX machine.

